Summary:

	Collaborative writing blog--- short stories are written by users of the blog--- users submit the next line of the short story and story is updated every 30 minutes~ with the most upvoted line being added to the story. Story has limit of lines. Every four lines~ there is a picture. 

	
COMPONENTS:

	POSTING

		Text box (limited number of characters) with post button

		When posted, adds the item to html display


	Display of the website

		HTML CSS

		Buttons

		Programemd in a way for infinite/dynamic 

	Interacting with the website



	Storing of the data on the website